<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>You Have Been Added to an Election</title>
    <style>
      * { box-sizing: border-box; } body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4; margin: 0; padding: 0; } .container { width:
      100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 1.5em auto; padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); }
      .header { text-align: center; padding: 20px 0; } .header h1 { margin: 0;
      color: #333333; } .content { margin: 20px 0; text-align: center; }
      .content p { color: #555555; line-height: 1.6; } .button { display:
      inline-block; padding: 12px 25px; background-color: #007bff; color:
      #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
      .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; padding: 10px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid #dddddd; color: #aaaaaa; } .logo { max-width: 120px;
      margin-bottom: 20px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <img
          src="https://storage.googleapis.com/aminmakes/logo.png"
          alt="Company Logo"
          class="logo"
        />
        <h1>Election Notification</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
        <p>We are pleased to inform you that you have been successfully added as
          a voter for the upcoming election:
          <strong>{{electionName}}</strong>.</p>
        <p>The election is scheduled to begin on
          <strong>{{startDate}}</strong>
          and will end on
          <strong>{{endDate}}</strong>.</p>
        <p>You will receive a reminder when voting opens.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please feel free to
          reach out to our support team.</p>
        <a href="{{confirmationLink}}" class="button">Visit Voting Dashboard</a>
        <p>Thank you for participating in shaping the future of our
          organization!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Best regards, <br />Votes Team</p>
        <p>
          <img
            src="https://storage.googleapis.com/aminmakes/footer.webp"
            alt="Footer Image"
            class="logo"
          />
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>